{"tid":1686553,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"11 月 24 日全民孝順日，人人蛇齋餅粽！","createTime":"2019-11-01T08:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T10:12:53.000Z","uid":275006,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"339dd6066f6abedde7fdb7bb3cbce077afd01b4b","tid":1686553,"uid":275006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11 月 24 日全民孝順日，人人蛇齋餅粽！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>區選救港，全民敬老：自己屋企自己救！</strong></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n很多人說，不要理會區選了，會輸的，你怎麼跟掌心雷和旅遊巴鬥？的確，根據往年的經驗，每次選舉，幾乎每個老人院都會有一車車旅遊巴，把院友們一個個送到票站，媒體也多次發現投票的長者手上都有著一張投票指示。<br />\n<br />\n根據選民登記數據，很多區的選民資料都出現一個很奇怪的現象，就是 70 歲以上選民數字特別高，當然 60 歲以上也很多。故此很多時候，即使該區是建制派素人參選，也很容易高票當選。不難猜，數字裡的許多長者都是被登記和被投票的，當然也有許多是被矇騙或真心相信才投票的。<br />\n<br />\n有些選區的情況非常嚴峻，<ins><strong><em>比如說 R20 大圍。這個選區目前有 12,731 位選民，其中 61 歲以上的選民最多，佔整體選民數目達 40.7%，即有 5,000 個長者選民。這個數字看來非常不尋常，不過區内有幾家安老院，估計可能院友們都被登記為選民；此外美林邨也有不少長者。<br />\n</em></strong></ins><br />\n院舍管理方一般都是把長者的重要私人物品收起，包括身份證等，故此如果有人買起院舍姑娘，她就能把所有的院友登記選民，然後再在投票日當天......就是我們看到的掌心雷和旅遊巴。許多老人院和某些政治組織都有著多年的合作經驗。<br />\n<br />\n這樣看來，我們似乎沒法破掌心雷和旅遊巴？<br />\n<br />\n真的嗎？<br />\n<br />\n不，有一招或許可破，但要每個人一起做，一個字：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">孝</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>11月24日，香港救亡日，全民孝順日。</strong>我們一早起床去<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>接我們的長輩</ins></span></span></strong></strong></span></strong>，<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>記得從某些人手中奪回屬於老人家的身份證</ins></span></span></strong></strong>，再一起去飲茶，然後<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>再帶他們去票站</ins></span></span></span></strong>。但我們也不要讓人說我們當天才孝順，從現在開始，和已經住在院舍的長輩們多聊天，分享最近香港在發生的事情，這些事情和他們年輕時經歷過的相比或許更可怕和荒謬，我們在如何努力，我們要如何一起拯救我們的香港，制裁喬裝暴徒，讓香港重回和諧。這樣，每人都要去做，每個區我們或許能救走幾百票，這樣已經可以決勝！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">區選救港，全民敬老：自己屋企自己！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dusvcwX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdusvcwX.jpg&h=0a8649d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dpG0zLj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdpG0zLj.jpg&h=8e4c843c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGjQWYG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGjQWYG.jpg&h=6c00597f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13ad797b01850fb40447810297a961644ff40779","tid":1686553,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"區選救港，全民敬老"},{"pid":"a5773b156eef1eb5aa68a7b307275549783880cd","tid":1686553,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:13:35.000Z","msg":"推呀！各位孝順仔女！"},{"pid":"5526238ee28e84baf622d6319277c9cd067c2def","tid":1686553,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"全民做孝子"},{"pid":"3d6ae39c509834b8e59067cfcc47a7696ef758bc","tid":1686553,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:13:58.000Z","msg":"做唔到蛇齋餅粽, 要幫藍絲長輩好好保管身份證<br />\n唔見左要補領好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d629fb4ddb408842d834ea213c7f93e356899b","tid":1686553,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:15:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">敬老救港</span>"},{"pid":"cc53ae0826c40d1d4a0f39330b9adef57fd87125","tid":1686553,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"種票先係重點"},{"pid":"10cfa0974f03c111d2c4131141dccd23640f9279","tid":1686553,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />票投民建聯，區選玩撚完"},{"pid":"6bfe3822d2277dc69ee4779506e240fe1d4ab27d","tid":1686553,"uid":72065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6da0185801f99747ebf8327f6df7ed03fb29cde","tid":1686553,"uid":324954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入則孝，出則弟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n陪伴老人家，拉埋兄弟姐妹參與全民孝順日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1629237dc3617664f867f4ac4f13e9e881d6a776","tid":1686553,"uid":10424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:24:51.000Z","msg":"岩！ 嗱 我地唔係唔俾老人家去投票呀！我地係接佢地去食餐飯 再同佢地一齊去投票！我地唔係干預老人家投票。去到票站佢中意投民建聯係佢既事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0ec3bc677464a428a2c7c11fc19fdb19278f0d","tid":1686553,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"963ead16e013c1c018d7aa23bbc267d086d94a74","tid":1686553,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d6ae39c509834b8e59067cfcc47a7696ef758bc","tid":1686553,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:13:58.000Z","msg":"做唔到蛇齋餅粽, 要幫藍絲長輩好好保管身份證<br />\n唔見左要補領好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:28:13.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多"},{"pid":"2d083f9ef93e8b1d4dcfa3193347f88c8d053c37","tid":1686553,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13ad797b01850fb40447810297a961644ff40779","tid":1686553,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"區選救港，全民敬老"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"各位要connect埋老人家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛民主，黎投票</span></span><br />\n區議會有好多野可以做，請幫幫手<br />\n贏左係籌碼，輸左係比人魚肉！<br />\nConnect 多d人，離開同溫層！<br />\n票票皆辛苦，多你一票就好多！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好push紅媒，睇壞腦</span></span>，多推蘋果立場<br />\n多推：行動、策略、活動、有效益post<br />\n少推：紅媒、分化、負面、低效益post<br />\n幫手諗下抗議仲可以點樣轉型？<br />\n有咩方法可以突破困局?<br />\n<br />\n5毛同警察合作天衣無縫<br />\n<strong>冇效益活動</strong>，下次就唔好比人帶到方向<br />\n連登五毛滲透嚴重，大家要帶腦睇post<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉專題研究之抗爭Project：<br />\n引導香港-啟蒙運動：<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">情緒主導&gt;理性主導</span></span><br />\n-點Push更多人投票？<br />\n-何謂民主、自由、公義、法治、公平？<br />\n-以上普世價值對大眾有咩好處？<br />\n-香港未來如何向前走？<br />\n<br />\n學習任務：<br />\n1.了解西方啓蒙運動前因後果<br />\n2.Search民主、自由、公義、法治、公平<br />\n3.將普世價值連結到香港人利益利益利益<br />\n4.走向獨裁/走向民主，主權在民<br />\n5.睇一次基本法<br />\n6.睇埋選舉條例<br />\n<br />\n活動：<br />\n落街、落區、開攤位、教育關心街坊<br />\n愛民主，黎投票；撐自由，齊發聲<br />\n為公義，企出黎；護法治，三分權<br />\n要公平，改制度；港未來，自己來<br />\n<br />\n我相信極權唔怕武力升級，卻怕頭腦升級，有更多人看穿一切的謊言，群起反抗！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Signature</span>簽名檔：守護香港，深層改革<br />\nVersion 2019.11.1 <span style=\"color: red;\"><em>愛民主，黎投票</em></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Be Water! Be Smart!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n抗爭轉型及進化建議：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰拖垮邪惡</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重要目標：</span></strong>11月24號區議會選舉<br />\n香港民主及人權法案<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">防範：</span></strong>掌心雷、利誘淺黃淺藍市民、抹黑<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式示威：</span></strong>警察舉旗咪去另一個地方示威，香港咁多地方可以去，佢想捉你，你咪話走緊囉，太多人行得慢好正常，合情合理合法！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">適當武力/自衛反擊：</span></strong>合情又合理！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">創意活動：抗爭融入生活</span></strong>唱歌比賽？跑步大叫？商場罷買？摺紙？18區和你傾、流水式返學返工#Shout4HK#諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：保持民意、減少被捕<br />\n建議：落街和你傾，離開同溫層！文宣！<br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化黃色陣營、黃色經濟圈<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、啓蒙思想<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMdiioB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMdiioB.jpg&h=7e10cb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨、新華社、環球時報、人民日報<br />\n2.誤導：警總救護車、雷射槍、9吋尖刀等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者/黑警：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法、恐嚇<br />\n12.利用親中人士發表「假」權威言論<br />\n13.高樓價掠奪民脂民膏<br />\n14.矮化示威者為甲由、yellow object<br />\n15.假對話，真緊急法：獨裁者2.0<br />\n16.高壓統治，嚇到你噤聲<br />\n17.黑社會X警方X中聯辦X政府X地產霸權<br />\n18.濫用法律/禁制令，以達到政治目的<br />\n19.警察X 5毛，低效益，假風向<br />\n諗到再加</span><br />\nSir, my concern is not whether God is on our side; my greatest concern is to be on God's side, for God is always right."},{"pid":"edbeb332f21f1702c53e0aea4a0e49c3e929a597","tid":1686553,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd468d87518c1299b83afbf17eccddcde01423e","tid":1686553,"uid":275006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc237fc35e53300cc81ea5673b9eda4f7c3d189","tid":1686553,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:07:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"096eaedb98d67c33e4bcfae979afa4f03e319820","tid":1686553,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屋企藍色既 就報個大陸 2日1夜團 送佢上去啦 屌"},{"pid":"4cd32237b26e6ef442ca97091cd3573b19a58a62","tid":1686553,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"甲由平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4f84176811215631255c5a9738ef83707ca374","tid":1686553,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"甲由平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef